import React from 'react'
import Contact_bread from './Contact_component/Contact_bread'
import Contact_form from './Contact_component/Contact_form'
import CounterTest from './Home_component/CounterTest'

const Contact = () => {
  return (
    <>
    <Contact_bread></Contact_bread>
    <Contact_form></Contact_form>
    <CounterTest nthNumber={100}></CounterTest>
    </>
  )
}

export default Contact
